Well, as the market is overloaded with so many different ICO's, we are planing to make some marketing tricks which will help us to stand out from the crowd.   Quote from: mixail09 on November 15, 2017, 09:37:03 PM I like the fact it's a startup but can you explain why have you chosen crypto and ICO for your project?  Quote from: yahman on November 15, 2017, 10:14:09 PM Hi, how exactly are you going to use smart contracts in your project? Since we are a mass consumer good, our community of investors can bring an extremely large network of connections which can become clients of Pressco. Besides that, if we perform extremely good, value of the token goes up giving us a long term funding.
